Subscribe for more GTLive action! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9 
Raging At New AGAR.IO Shooter- Diep.io ► http://bit.ly/1W3OKky
Size Does Matter! - Slitherio ►► http://bit.ly/1U8EP7z

The Quest for the Biggest mace has begun. And I will prove myself on the battlefield as I play the next Agar.io game. Sure historically I haven't been the best at these types of games, but this time it uses physics. How can I lose? Let's whack each other around with our maces and see how big we can get.
